<div class="containers">
  <div class="left-container">
    <div class="ls-card">
      <div class="top">
        <h2>Send us a Message</h2>
        <p>
          Fill out the form below and we'll get back to you as soon as possible
        </p>
      </div>

      <form>
        <!-- Row 1 -->
        <div class="name-input">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="fullName">Full Name *</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="fullName"
              formControlName="fullName"
              class="form-control input-style"
              placeholder="Enter your full name"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email"
              formControlName="email"
              class="form-control input-style"
              placeholder="Enter your email"
              required
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Row 2 -->
        <div class="name-input">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="phoneNumber">Phone Number</label>
            <input
              type="tel"
              id="phoneNumber"
              formControlName="phoneNumber"
              class="form-control input-style"
              placeholder="Enter your phone number"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="subject">Subject *</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="subject"
              formControlName="subject"
              class="form-control input-style"
              placeholder="What's this about?"
              required
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Message -->
        <div class="field">
          <label for="message">Message *</label>
          <textarea
            id="message"
            formControlName="message"
            class="form-control input-style textarea-style"
            placeholder="Tell us how we can help you..."
            required
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <!-- Submit Button -->
        <button type="submit" class="btn-signup submit">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq">
  <div class="top">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p>Quick answers to common questions</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card-container">
    <div class="card faq-card">
      <h3>How far in advance package should I book my trip?</h3>
      <p>
        For international destination, we recommend booking at least 2-3 months
        in advance. For domestic trips, 2-4 weeks is usually sufficient,
        depending on the season and destination.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card faq-card">
      <h3>What's included in your travel packages?</h3>
      <p>
        Our packages typically include accommodation, transportation, guided
        tours, and select meals. Specific inclusions vary by package and are
        clearly detailed on each package page.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card faq-card">
      <h3>Do you offer travel insurance?</h3>
      <p>
        Yes, we highly recommend travel insurance and can help you select the
        right coverage for your trip. We partner with trusted insurance
        providers to offer comprehensive protection.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="card faq-card">
      <h3>Can I customize my travel package?</h3>
      <p>
        Absolutely! We specialize in creating personalized travel experiences.
        Contact our team to discuss your preferences, and we'll tailor a package
        that meets your specific needs and interests.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
